'''Akaṛmus''' ([[Assaɣ usnan]]: ''Opuntia ficus-indica'') d [[talmest]] n [[imɣi|yemɣan]] yeṭṭafaren [[tawsit (tudersent)|tawsit]] n [[takaṛmust (tawsit)|ukarmus]] deg [[tawacult (tasnudert)|twacult]] n [[Tikaṛmusin|tkaṛmusin]], Akaṛmus yettemɣay deg yidgan [[Takewt|yekkawen]] ila (yesɛa) tazmert meqqren deg tudert deg yidgan dgi drusen (neqsen) [[aman|waman]] acku igeṭman-is ččuren d aman, Dɣa igeṭman-a d [[učči]] ira (iḥemmel) [[alɣem|welɣem]] deg [[taneẓruft|tneẓruft]] ɣas akken dges [[asennan n yemɣi|isennanen]] imesden.

== Aẓaṛ n ukaṛmus ==
Tamurt taẓaṛant n ukaṛmus d [[Tamrikt n Ugafa]] sin akin yedda ar tamiwin n iden n umadal deg [[awines wis 16|uwines wis 16]] seg [[Turuft|Uruppa]] ar Idgan n iden, Akarmus d win yettilin deg [[Tafriqt n ugafa|Tefrikt n ugafa]] aladɣa deg [[Tamurt n Leqbayel|Tmurt n Iqbayliyen]] 

